data.title: Madonna teamed up with electronic music producer William Orbit to craft "Beautiful Stranger" for the "Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged...
data.meta_description:
1,470 likes, 42 comments - crave_madonna on March 2, 2024: "Madonna teamed up with electronic music producer William Orbit to craft "Beautiful Stranger" for the "Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me" soundtrack. 

Released in 1999, the song was chosen by the album's executive producers to promote the soundtrack and became a hit, reaching number one in several countries. It also holds a special place in Madonna's discography, appearing on three of her greatest hits collections.
